{"id":232336160,"title":"#講座課程 創作過程踩到紅線了嗎？","content":"【2019 大專院校藝術科系法律教育規劃】\n\n此次計畫是教育部為促進藝術創作相關科系學生對於智慧財權的認識及相關權利保障。\n \n法務於非相關類科學生而言可能相對陌生，但智財權益對於創作者而言不可輕視，為宣導避免有侵權等事件發生，且希望創作者可有效利用智慧財產權所賦予的權利取得自己應得的成果，並透過工作坊累積實務經驗。\n \n以下是此次計畫的相關資訊：\n預計以講座形式舉辦「文創產學媒合與智財議題工作坊」\n\n時間：10/26(六) 9:30~17:00\n地點：東海大學-產學大樓 2F 想創空間\n  臺中西屯區臺灣大道四段1727號\nhttps://i.imgur.com/fBtdbPY.jpg\n費用：免費，提供餐點\n活動粉專：\nhttps://reurl.cc/NaRZln\n報名連結：\nhttps://reurl.cc/pD1R1d\n\n第一場講座活動的媒體報導：\nhttps://www.cool3c.com/article/148597","excerpt":"【2019 大專院校藝術科系法律教育規劃】此次計畫是教育部為促進藝術創作相關科系學生對於智慧財權的認識及相關權利保障。法務於非相關類科學生而言可能相對陌生，但智財權益對於創作者而言不可輕視，為宣導避免","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"2bb20844-07ec-41d3-830f-ae551fc31246","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-10-20T08:25:54.883Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-20T08:25:54.883Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":3,"tags":[],"topics":["講座","智慧財產權"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"課程","forumAlias":"course","school":"國立臺北大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":2},{"id":"aa0d425f-d530-4478-9a77-fe3aedc79eea","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/fBtdbPY.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"bf6eae58-732c-412f-a371-bdfc5fac774f","url":"https://i.imgur.com/fBtdbPYl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/fBtdbPYl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/fBtdbPYl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-20T08:25:54.883Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-20T08:25:54.883Z"},{"id":"bf6eae58-732c-412f-a371-bdfc5fac774f","url":"https://i.imgur.com/fBtdbPY.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/fBtdbPY","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/fBtdbPYl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-20T0